DotnetProcessAppdomainThreadContext <br/>
<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/youngmtool/csharpdotnet/master/pics/DotnetProcessAppdomainThreadContext2.png"> <br/><br/>

o Active threads can be moved to other AppDomains and Context boundaries by the CLR to fit the perfomance.<br/>
But it's impossible for a single thread to be working in more than one AppDomain at once.


